messages.subject: RE: [UnschoolingDiscussion] pregnancy dreams
messages.msgSnippet: My pregnancy dreams are weird.  They have been the same topic roughly each time.  Dan Marino (football guy) is running through my dreams trying to kill me?
messages.messageBody:
My pregnancy dreams are weird. They have been the same topic roughly each
time. Dan Marino (football guy) is running through my dreams trying to kill
me?
Weird? I don't even watch football or any other sport. HMMMM>>>>>
Another one is I am lying on the side of a pool in a recliner lawnchair and
having repeated orgasms.
Analysis anyone?

Kim Flowers - Wife to Nolan & Mama of 3

"And I mean X rated, clear as a bell, and darned good, too."

Oh yeah...same here. I had the weird baby dreams too.
The only time I've had lesbian tendencies was during pregnancy (and only in
my sleeping dreams) so analyze THAT one.?
That's some kinda hormone thing to be sure. The second and third trimesters
are sexually charged for me every time! But it's a little harder to fulfill
sexual fantasies when you're the size of a small whale. :)
